item.title: So, you think you know me...?
item.author: ICSM RAG Fashion Show Team '19,
item.description: What we’re doing The ICSM RAG ‘You Know My Name’ Fashion Show 2019, held at The Clapham Grand on 12th March, is the most exuberant fundraising event hosted by the Medical School. The evening entails a decadent display of unique fashion, donated by twelve up-and-coming designers, and modelled by …
